text: Doubutsu Sentai Zyuohger is a Japanese television series. It is the 40th in Toei's Super Sentai series. Super Hero Time joined Kamen Rider Ghost and then Kamen Rider Ex-Aid. ==Characters== ===Zyuohger=== Actor Name Rangers Cube Masaki Nakao Yamato Kazariki Zyuoh Eagle Cube Eagle, Cube Gorilla, Cube Whale Miki Yanagi Sela Zyuoh Shark Cube Shark Shohei Nanba Leo Zyuoh Lion Cube Lion Tsurugi Watanabe Tusk Zyuoh Elephant Cube Elephant Haruka Tateishi Amu Zyuoh Tiger Cube Tiger Naoki Kunishima Misao Mondo Zyuoh The World Cube Rhino, Cube Crocodile, Cube Wolf Kohei Murakami Bud Zyuoh Bird Cube Kamonohashi, Cube Hyou, Cube Fukurou, Cube Shimauma ==Cast== * Yamato Kazakiri / Zyuoh Eagle: Masaki Nakao * Sela / Zyuoh Shark: Miki Yanagi * Leo / Zyuoh Lion: Shohei Nanba * Tusk / Zyuoh Elephant: Tsurugi Watanabe * Amu / Zyuoh Tiger: Haruka Tateishi * Misao Mondo / Zyuoh The World: Naoki Kunshima * Bud / Zyuoh Bird: Kohei Murakami * Mario Mori: Susumu Terajima ===Voice Actors=== * Larry (Voice): Unshō Ishizuka * Rhino Man (Voice): Volcano Ōta * Crocodile Man (Voice): Mitsuaki Kanuka * Wolf Man (Voice): Hidenori Takahashi * Cetus (Voice): Chō * Narration, Zyuohger Equipment Voice: Chō ===Guest cast=== * Takeru Tenkūji (7): Shun Nishime * Yurusen (Voice) (7): Aoi Yūki * Genkuro Oiwa (12): Masashi Horiuchi * Marin Fuwa (14): Ayana Shiramoto * Captain Marvelous / Gokai Red (28, 29): Ryota Ozawa * Joe Gibken / Gokai Blue (28, 29): Yuki Yamada * Luka Millfy / Gokai Yellow (28, 29): Mao Ichimichi * Don Dogoier / Gokai Green (28, 29): Kazuki Shimizu * Ahim de Famille / Gokai Pink (28, 29): Yui Koike * Gai Ikari / Gokai Silver (28, 29): Junya Ikeda * Navi (Voice) (28, 29): Yukari Tamura * Mobilate (Voice) (28, 29): Tomokazu Seki * Boy (38): Hikari Tobita * Rei (39): Hiroaki Iwanaga * Kageyuki Kazakiri (42, 45-Finale): Tomiyuki Kunihiro * Reporter (43): Minase Yashiro ==Songs== ;
